<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Learn-Software.com – Aggregation</title><link>http://localhost:1313/tags/aggregation/</link><description>Recent content in Aggregation on Learn-Software.com</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="http://localhost:1313/tags/aggregation/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Aggregation</title><link>http://localhost:1313/programming/oop/class-relations/aggregation/</link><pubDate>Sat, 12 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://localhost:1313/programming/oop/class-relations/aggregation/</guid><description>
&lt;img src="http://localhost:1313/programming/oop/class-relations/aggregation/featured.en_hu_931f308e6dff1ae.jpg" width="640" height="426"/>&lt;p&gt;Key characteristics of aggregation:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s a stronger relationship than a simple association, but weaker than composition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The &amp;ldquo;part&amp;rdquo; object can exist independently of the &amp;ldquo;whole&amp;rdquo; object.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple &amp;ldquo;whole&amp;rdquo; objects can share the same &amp;ldquo;part&amp;rdquo; object.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If the &amp;ldquo;whole&amp;rdquo; object is destroyed, the &amp;ldquo;part&amp;rdquo; object continues to exist.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&amp;rsquo;s look at an example to illustrate aggregation:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code"&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Department&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;__init__&lt;/span&gt;(self, name):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; name
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;employees &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; []
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;add_employee&lt;/span&gt;(self, employee):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;employees&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append(employee)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;remove_employee&lt;/span&gt;(self, employee):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;employees&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;remove(employee)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;list_employees&lt;/span&gt;(self):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Department &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; has employees: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;join(emp&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; emp &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;employees)&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Employee&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;__init__&lt;/span&gt;(self, name, id):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; name
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;id &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; id
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;__str__&lt;/span&gt;(self):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;f&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Employee(name=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;name&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;, id=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;self&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;id&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;)&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Creating instances&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hr_dept &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Department(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Human Resources&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;it_dept &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Department(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Information Technology&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;emp1 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Employee(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;E001&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;emp2 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Employee(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Bob&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;E002&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;emp3 &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Employee(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Charlie&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;E003&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Adding employees to departments&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hr_dept&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;add_employee(emp1)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hr_dept&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;add_employee(emp2)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;it_dept&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;add_employee(emp2) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Note: Bob works in both HR and IT&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;it_dept&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;add_employee(emp3)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(hr_dept&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;list_employees())
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(it_dept&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;list_employees())
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# If we remove the HR department, the employees still exist&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;del&lt;/span&gt; hr_dept
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(emp1) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Employee still exists&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0"&gt;
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
aria-label="Copy code"
data-copied-label="Copied!"
&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this example, we have an aggregation relationship between &lt;code&gt;Department&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;Employee&lt;/code&gt;. A &lt;code&gt;Department&lt;/code&gt; has &lt;code&gt;Employee&lt;/code&gt;s, but &lt;code&gt;Employee&lt;/code&gt;s can exist independently of any particular &lt;code&gt;Department&lt;/code&gt;. Also, an &lt;code&gt;Employee&lt;/code&gt; can belong to multiple &lt;code&gt;Department&lt;/code&gt;s (as we see with Bob).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s a UML diagram representing this aggregation relationship:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div role="img" aria-label="Diagram"&gt;
&lt;pre class="mermaid hx:mt-6"&gt;
classDiagram
class Department {
+name: string
+employees: list
+add_employee(employee)
+remove_employee(employee)
+list_employees()
}
class Employee {
+name: string
+id: string
+__str__()
}
Department o-- Employee : has
end
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;In this diagram, the open diamond on the &lt;code&gt;Department&lt;/code&gt; side of the relationship indicates aggregation. This shows that &lt;code&gt;Department&lt;/code&gt; is the &amp;ldquo;whole&amp;rdquo; and &lt;code&gt;Employee&lt;/code&gt; is the &amp;ldquo;part&amp;rdquo; in this relationship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s important to note that while aggregation implies a whole-part relationship, the &amp;ldquo;part&amp;rdquo; (in this case, &lt;code&gt;Employee&lt;/code&gt;) can exist independently and can even be part of multiple &amp;ldquo;wholes&amp;rdquo; (multiple &lt;code&gt;Department&lt;/code&gt;s).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;div class="hx:overflow-x-auto hx:mt-6 hx:flex hx:rounded-lg hx:border hx:py-2 hx:ltr:pr-4 hx:rtl:pl-4 hx:contrast-more:border-current hx:contrast-more:dark:border-current hx:border-green-200 hx:bg-green-100 hx:text-green-900 hx:dark:border-green-200/30 hx:dark:bg-green-900/30 hx:dark:text-green-200"&gt;
